reasoning_judge: The ground truth describes several specific visual bugs: enemy legs clipping through a lamppost, unnaturally twisted limbs, and an enemy being projected into (and clipping inside) a truck. The generated bug report explicitly states that there are "no visible glitches or strange behaviors" and that everything looks fine. This is the exact opposite of the ground-truth description, so they are clearly not referring to the same bug.
